Class Card

java.lang.Object
Card
public class Card
extends java.lang.Object

Card class

this class input 1 number and convert it to specific type and color for cards
have getExist method to return card exit in box or not have getColor method to return ID of color card have getType method to return type of cards have getIdCard method to return number of card in box for remove and add to box have setExit method to remove and card from box have setColor method to change "changeColor" card when player use it
